Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Long, long ago, one night,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the Moon disappeared from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Tree plunged into darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad, where are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys listening to me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, the Moon reappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but the hero was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, there will be another total lunar eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Tree will be in total darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,total lunar eclipses cause Energy Seeds to lose their light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and their energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you must find fireflies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and borrow their light,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so that during the total lunar eclipse,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we can keep the Energy Seed glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s hurry and find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Borrowing the fireflies’ light?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard Wolffy’s voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry; I set up some traps earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If he arrives, he’ll surely be launched away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the fireflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for rescuing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you being so careless,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cockroach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I’m not a cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re a lychee bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,may I ask if you know where I can find
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,fireflies that can glow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s pitch-black in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s nothing here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle, they look the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that the lychee bugs nowadays can also glow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m a firefly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you’re a firefly, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d like to borrow your light to help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He can’t help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I’m a firefly that can’t glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not even allowed to attend firefly parties!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can’t you glow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t glowed since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,my grandpa once glowed during a total lunar eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and rescued a lot of insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody believes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that you can glow just like your grandpa did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do I glow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really have to jump that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Going beyond your limits is what fuels your instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind; I actually don’t really want to go to the parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s too loud there; it’s not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the party outfit you’ve urged for a month has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ticket, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Only fireflies that can glow are allowed to enter the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The total lunar eclipse is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we found fireflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where the fireflies have their evening parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I capture the fireflies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the goats will come to me and fall right into my trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed a firefly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it’s a bug that can’t glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle! Twinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the other fireflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A big, evil wolf captured them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that he overheard us talking about borrowing firefly light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go save my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything’s ready; just waiting for the goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m here to rescue you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We were mean to you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go; don’t let Wolffy find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I must rescue you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s you again, you glowless bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, let Twinkle go right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome; the total lunar eclipse is finally starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s see how you’ll escape when it’s this dark out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t tell where the boulder is coming from!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can… I can glow…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s strange; why does the boulder keep following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,look at your headlights!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When did those get on my train?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been when Wolffy did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the Energy Seed is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My Energy Seed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle, thank you for rescuing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re a true firefly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, Twinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
